videos.description: Oregon State's Gary Payton II cleans up a mess with the quick steal, and with an open lane to the hoop, throws down a vicious two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Gary Payton II with quick steal and monster slam

videos.description: Oregon State forgets to box out Colorado's Wesley Gordon, leaving him an open lane to slam home the missed shot with a vicious one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Gordon out of nowhere for huge putback slam
